                "text": "When a vidgamer scores a critical hit against a creature within 60 feet, they can also attempt an Intimidate check to demoralize that creature as a reaction before the end of their turn. When a vidgamer rolls a natural 20 for a Profession (vidgamer) check to play a game, they can also attempt to demoralize one other participant in that game as a reaction before the end of their turn.",
